    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The library is really good. It has different collections for various genres. We can even get the college notes through library because the professors themselves also curates the library.",
          "name": "Gauri Nair",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college is located in an excellent area, most people are helpful and the vibe is chill. It's not stressful regarding attendance or marks. The crowd especially for Arts is quite good and you will find some great people here.",
          "name": "Saamya joiya",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "St Andrews also has a good library with a wide range of books to use and also take home after permission And also the curriculum along with the course are quite decent and so are the exams if u read the material well and a decent fee range as well",
          "name": "Melania almeida",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "St Andrews also has a good wide range of departments to select from and join into which helps in  strengthening ur social skills and also gain experience",
          "name": "Melania almeida",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "St Andrews is among the good Colleges in Mumbai for arts science and commerce I selected arts in my undergraduate degree and am planning to study psychology and become a psychologist Andrews has a good faculty and good facility along with their staff",
          "name": "Melania almeida",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college professors indulge in giving us the best knowledge in their field",
          "name": "Aaron Dias",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teaching faculty are very friendly and think for the betterment of the students",
          "name": "Aaron Dias",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teaching was good i liked it . The faculties are helpful they will help you understand the concepts",
          "name": "Drushti",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus life is quite good , the people there have a standard and they are good .",
          "name": "Drushti",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "I really liked the college campus and sports facilites students can play football,  badminton , and basket ball they have a basketball court , really liked it.",
          "name": "Drushti",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "The canteen is empty a lot of times and there aren't many good affordable options I think they need to work on that",
          "name": "Saamya joiya",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "felt like they reinforce Christian propaganda subtly in lectures but I guess that everyone now",
          "name": "Saamya joiya",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "some teachers are mean and don't finish their portions until the very last minute",
          "name": "Saamya joiya",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "I wish however St Andrews had a singleMajor in psychology as it does not offer that it offers a double major in psychology and if u wish to be a psychologist u do require the single major in psychology",
          "name": "Melania almeida",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The college doens't have lift forr students for reaching 4 floors",
          "name": "Aaron Dias",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The lecture timings for self financed course are very exhausting",
          "name": "Aaron Dias",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "One thing i dont like about the college us they charge for the events in the college like the events should be free atleast for the college people , they charge like 800 or 1k rupees, which i dont like at all",
          "name": "Drushti",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The placement services are not that good i dont have much information about that.",
          "name": "Drushti",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "They dont have lifts accessible to students , it makes difficult for us to climb 4 floors everyday.",
          "name": "Drushti",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        }
      ]
    },
